org.sandag.popsyn.domain
Class Household

java.lang.Object
  org.sandag.popsyn.domain.Household
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Household>, org.sandag.common.montecarlo.IWeight, IHousehold
public class Household
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHousehold, org.sandag.common.montecarlo.IWeight, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Household>

This class represents the households and group quarters in PopSyn. Each Household object is mapped to a PUMS record in the database. This mapping is carried out by ReaderDao and Household.xml
